\c 17
\s Ukuqiniswa kombuso kaJehoshafathi
\p
\v 1 UJehoshafathi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe; waziqinisa ukumelana loIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 15.24.\x*.
\v 2 Wasebeka amabutho kuyo yonke imizi ebiyelweyo yakoJuda\x + 19.5. 17.19. 11.5.\x*; wabeka lamabutho enqaba elizweni lakoJuda\x + 1 Sam. 10.5.\x*, lemizini yakoEfrayimi uyise uAsa ayeyithumbile\x + 15.8. 13.19.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisiba loJehoshafathi, ngoba wahamba ngendlela zakuqala zikaDavida uyise, kabadinganga oBhali;
\v 4 kodwa wadinga kuNkulunkulu kayise, wahamba ngemilayo yakhe\x + 1 Kho. 22.43.\x*, njalo kungenjengokwenza kukaIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 12.28.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yawuqinisa umbuso esandleni sakhe, loJuda wonke waletha izipho kuJehoshafathi\x + 17.11. 32.23. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*; wasesiba lenotho lodumo ngobunengi\x + 18.1.\x*.
\v 6 Inhliziyo yakhe yasiphakama ezindleleni zeN\nd kosi\nd*; futhi-ke wasusa indawo eziphakemeyo\x + 15.17. 20.33. 1 Kho. 22.43.\x* lezixuku koJuda\x + 19.3.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Langomnyaka wesithathu wokubusa kwakhe wathuma kuziphathamandla zakhe, kuBeni-Hayili lakuObhadiya lakuZekhariya lakuNethaneli lakuMikhaya, ukufundisa emizini yakoJuda.
\v 8 Kanye lazo-ke amaLevi, oShemaya loNethaniya loZebhadiya loAsaheli loShemiramothi loJehonathani loAdonija loTobija loTobi-Adonija, amaLevi\x + 15.3. 35.3. Ezra 7.10. Neh. 8.7.\x*; kanye labo-ke oElishama loJehoramu, abapristi\x + 15.3. 35.3. Ezra 7.10. Neh. 8.7.\x*.
\v 9 Basebefundisa koJuda, belogwalo lomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*; babhoda kuyo yonke imizi yakoJuda, bafundisa abantu.
\p
\v 10 Kwasekusiba lokuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* phezu kwayo yonke imibuso yamazwe ayehanqe uJuda, okokuthi kayilwanga loJehoshafathi\x + 14.14. 20.29.\x*.
\v 11 La\add banye\add* bamaFilisti\x + 21.16.\x* bamlethela uJehoshafathi\x + 26.8. 2 Sam. 8.2.\x* izipho\x + 17.11. 32.23. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*, lesiliva lokuthela; amaArabhiya lawo amlethela imihlambi, inqama eziyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lamakhulu ayisikhombisa, lezimpongo eziyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lamakhulu ayisikhombisa\x + 21.16.\x*.
\p
\v 12 UJehoshafathi wayelokhu ekhula njalo\x + 1 Sam. 2.26.\x*, waze waba sengqongeni. Wasesakha koJuda izinqaba lemizi yeziphala\x + Eks. 1.11.\x*.
\v 13 Wayelomsebenzi omnengi emizini yakoJuda, lamadoda empi, amaqhawe alamandla, eJerusalema.
\v 14 Lala ngamanani awo ngezindlu zaboyise: KoJuda, induna zezinkulungwane, uAdina engumphathi, njalo kanye laye amaqhawe alamandla azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amathathu;
\v 15 leceleni kwakhe uJohanani umphathi, njalo kanye laye izinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili;
\v 16 leceleni kwakhe uAmasiya indodana kaZikiri, owazinikela ngesihle eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, njalo kanye laye amaqhawe alamandla azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili\x + Hlu. 5.2,9. Neh. 11.2.\x*.
\v 17 LakoBhenjamini: UEliyada iqhawe elilamandla, njalo kanye laye izinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili, ezihlome ngedandili langesihlangu\x + 1 Lan. 12.2.\x*;
\v 18 leceleni kwakhe uJehozabadi, njalo kanye laye izinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili, abahlomele impi\x + 1 Lan. 12.23,24. Nani 31.5.\x*.
\v 19 Laba babesebenzela inkosi ngaphandle kwalabo inkosi eyayibabeke emizini ebiyelweyo kuye wonke uJuda\x + 17.2.\x*.